ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#160: FILE: drivers/misc/ibmasm/remote.c:257:
+	if ((ret = input_register_device(mouse_dev)))

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

